title: Eat Co
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Western, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Opened fall-2014 an all vegan eatery besides Fellini Italian restaurant. Serves food like pita pockets, Thalis, burgers, shwarma, and soups. Has fresh bread, juices, smoothies, salads, house-made spreads and dips. Also sells protein powder, supplements, yoga wear, and jewelry. Confirmed open, Jan 2016.
streetAddress: main road of Sri Thanu Village
